HEADWORD: Runway
<hw>Run"way`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
channel of a stream.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The beaten path made by deer or other animals in
passing to and from their feeding grounds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

